##
## History
##
@node History History

  V1.2  (07-10-96)
  o You can view the script and clear it if you want.
  o ScriptFTP searchs the line to define the columms: name /dir /size
    comment. So the line didn't need to be the third as before.
    So, every RECENT file can be used, i hope :-)
  o The RECENT is add only one time. ScriptFTP check if it is already
    present; then delete it, and add it again if the option is marked
  o You can now add or not the EOL after each selection;it's a option
    in the Prefs.
  o It is now localised.

  V1.1  (04-05-96)
  o .readme can be add to the script by ScriptFTP
  o RECENT can be add to the script by ScriptFTP
  o ScriptFTP read the third line of the recent file to know where starts
    the columm of file, directory, size and readme.

  V1.0  (04-02-96)
  o First Release.


@endnode

